1. *Odnos* između Srbije i Crne Gore je sve bliži. (The relationship between Serbia and Montenegro is getting closer.)

2. *Odnos* između ljudi je važan za zajednicu. (The relationship between people is important for the community.)

3. U nedostatku *odnosa* sa okolinom, ljudi postaju usamljeni. (Without relationships with the environment, people become lonely.)

4. *Odnosi* između naroda mogu biti obojeni političkim neslaganjima. (Relations between nations can be colored by political disagreements.)

5. Jedna od najvažnijih stvari u vezi sa *odnosima* je poverenje. (One of the most important things in relation to relationships is trust.)